{"tid":2343926,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"山頂猛鬼屋 - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-12-28T09:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T00:34:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cb38485f1265c68e82f9b152c92a2e79c30e96ba","tid":2343926,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:52:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201228/SIKGTAITYFGKJIGBR22N45QBYI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201228%2FSIKGTAITYFGKJIGBR22N45QBYI%2F&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd54W3gw9R4Gr2eBBN4Jm0fY%3D&h=5db6959d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201228%2FSIKGTAITYFGKJIGBR22N45QBYI%2F&h=d09a5d90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201228/SIKGTAITYFGKJIGBR22N45QBYI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n山頂猛鬼屋 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Jf24i1oA51eojcI3xnxfk99LJsU=/875x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VQYB2JY7OZHIPLK5S2PK6NJFSM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJf24i1oA51eojcI3xnxfk99LJsU%3D%2F875x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVQYB2JY7OZHIPLK5S2PK6NJFSM.png&h=60eca98b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《倩女幽魂》<br />\n<br />\n重看《閃靈》後兩日，到朋友家作客聊天，無緣無故聽到鬼故事。事發於多年前山頂僑福道豪宅，朋友認識男主角，並非道聽途說。簡言之，男主角搬入首晚，半夜一個女人即爬上床來，躺在他身旁並提出做愛，名副其實急色鬼，且晚晚如是，夜夜痴纏。<br />\n<br />\n同場一朋友問：「乜樣㗎？會唔會係清朝女鬼呢？」我也插嘴：「似王祖賢都可以考慮噃。」朋友說：「發你個夢啦王祖賢！聽佢講女鬼嘅樣，係七十年代電視藝員嗰種化妝，唔係清朝。」怎知道不是男主角精神病？朋友說不是，因為連他的家人也見到，有時房門還自動關上，恐怖到極點。咁點算？朋友說：「當然係搬！仲可以點算？」逃跑雖可恥但有用，想起《閃靈》結局，也是母子倆慌忙逃離酒店。<br />\n<br />\n雖說「人生如戲，戲如人生」，但人生何以不是沒完沒了的《家有囍事》，而偏偏是《閃靈》呢？《閃靈》弦外之音是「種族清洗」，香港則有寫在牆上的「留島不留人」。Jack嘴巴說最愛兒子，決不傷他，轉頭卻拿起斧頭追殺九條街，未免太似聲稱很愛年輕人的特首了。<br />\n<br />\n最巧合的一幕，是Jack和惡鬼Grady（他生前殺掉妻子和兩個幼女）的對話。Grady問Jack：「你知道你兒子正嘗試讓外人介入這兒的事情嗎？」。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n《閃靈》戲劇原型，或可追溯到。。。。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"e857006ec64c37f28b2d131d6e9f4cf28971db4d","tid":2343926,"uid":18587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:55:17.000Z","msg":"係咪有地窂個間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"149172da68296e0c4c0fbe74b423bcb4b1c0b2ba","tid":2343926,"uid":84013,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e857006ec64c37f28b2d131d6e9f4cf28971db4d","tid":2343926,"uid":18587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:55:17.000Z","msg":"係咪有地窂個間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T10:08:50.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講多啲<br />\n<br />\n完全唔知"},{"pid":"5a49a06116204c9761d352108bd7abc49e70935e","tid":2343926,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T00:34:54.000Z","msg":"其實佢信乜嘢, 睇風水, 講鬼故, 信因果, 但唔信扶乩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}